{
  "stem": "8892.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, you know, we started to learn all the Latin with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew a lot of Latin at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, in the choir, they needed more girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember that-- there was a last grade, like in the eighth grade-- my mother let me be in a choir.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went into the Catholic church, because we were in already before, because they were not that-- my father was not that strict that I-- I did what the crowd did.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was so proud that I could join them in a choir and sing in a church that I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That I belonged, like, you know, I was in a group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You felt it, but you didn't-- you didn't think about it that much, because when there was homework, I was doing it with a Gentile girl.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was better in arithmetic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I helped her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went to their house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They always would give us, like, cookie and all, and they knew that I was allowed to eat that or a glass of milk or something like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they would come to our house, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But-- and doing homework, because that-- certain things when I was better, and I helped her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And her name was Eva, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they were nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But when Christmas came, I used to be so envious, because all the gifts they would get.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, you know, in Europe we didn't do such a big deal out of Hanukkah like in here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "All we had is dreidel and a few pennies, and then we played the dreidel all, you know, seven days and light the candles.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
